.TH "snd_hda_check_amp_caps" 9 "snd_hda_check_amp_caps" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
snd_hda_check_amp_caps \- query AMP capabilities
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" snd_hda_check_amp_caps
.BI "(struct hda_codec *codec "  ","
.BI "hda_nid_t nid "  ","
.BI "int dir "  ","
.BI "unsigned int bits "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "codec" 12
the HD-audio codec
.IP "nid" 12
the NID to query
.IP "dir" 12
either #HDA_INPUT or #HDA_OUTPUT
.IP "bits" 12
bit mask to check the result
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Check whether the widget has the given amp capability for the direction.
